snippet: Tommy Gainey and Johnson Wagner each shot an eight-under-par 62 to share a two-stroke lead after the first round of the Greenbrier Classic in White Sulphur Springs, W.Va.
abstract: Tommy Gainey and Johnson Wagner each shoot an eight-under-par 62 to share a two-stroke lead after the first round of the Greenbrier Classic in West Virginia's White Sulphur Springs.
